text.tspan: Share of clinical trials that report results within a year, 2021
Sponsors of clinical trials are required to report their results to the European Clinical Trials Register (EU-CTR) within
a year of completion, but many fail to do so. This shows the share of trials by non commercial sponsors reported on
Note: Data are not shown for multinational trials, or countries with fewer than 5 trials due for reporting.
